# SSE Payapl Oauth

## Paypal App Registration

Before you use our Oauth you need `clientId` and `clientSecret`. For getting it. There are few steps

1. Visit [Paypal developers](https://developer.paypal.com/) dashboard.
2. Log into the Developer Dashboard.
3. From **Apps & Credentials**, select your app.
   ![App & cred](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
4. Under **Other features**, select the **Log in with PayPal** checkbox and then select **Advanced Settings**.
   ![Login Paypal](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
5. Enter a **Return URL**. Your website or app redirects your users to this URL after they complete the Log in with PayPal flow.

## Usage

```tsx
import { PaypalIconButton } from "@sse-auth/react";

const onSucc = (accessToken: string | object, userData: UserProps) => {
  console.log(accessToken);
  console.log(userData);
  alert(
    `Logged in successfully! Welcome, ${userData.name}, global_name: ${userData.global_name}!`
  );
};

const onFail = (error: Error) => {
  console.error(error);
};

<PaypalIconButton
  clientId="YOUR_CLIENT_ID"
  clientSecret="YOUR_CLIENT_SECRET"
  onSuccess={onSucc}
  onFailure={onFail}
  sandbox
/>;
```
